              <h2>Hyper-V Hosting from VSS Business Solutions</h2>
              <p>Together with Microsoft, VSS Business Solutions is able to offer you the latest in hypervisor-based server virtualization technology: Hyper-V. A Hyper-V hosting solution enables you to run multiple operating systems on a single physical server as virtual machines (VMs). Why is this beneficial? Deploying multiple isolated virtual machines instead of physical servers means a lower total cost of ownership to you. Additionally, Hyper-V can help you optimize asset utilization and balance workloads across different resources.</p>
